text: Palestinian Medical Relief Society (PMRS) is a community based non-profit health-organization in Palestine. It was established in 1979 by a group of Palestinian doctors and health professionals. Its main objective is to improve the overall physical, mental, and social well being of all Palestinians, irrespective of their racial, political, social, economic status. ==References== Category:1979 establishments in Asia Category:Non-profit organizations of Asia Category:Organizations based in Palestine
title: Palestinian Medical Relief Society
